        <abstract>
            <p>Has heard that Louis Agassiz maintains the doctrine of several species of man "much I daresay to the comfort of the slave-holding southerners".</p>
            <p>Homeopathy excites his wrath even more than clairvoyance.</p>
        </abstract>
